title: Apparently I did not do enough damage

embed.description: Every game is a story; visit the new League of Legends match history to check out how this one ends and share your own!

body: According to Shen I should have done more damage.

replies.body: Hell yeah you could! Then again, this is poro king. SO WHO CARES? Was Shen salty or something or were you just bragging about your damage? ARAM is not a good testing ground/example pool for damage in most circumstances. Maybe in some specific ones but not everything.
